{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Iſtijus tahs\nGrahmatas no to Weſtneschu\nRohkas dabbuja/ un tahs laſ-\nſtis gahje wiſch ta KUNGA\nNaunā/ un Iſtijus ieplattija\ntahs preeſch ta KUNGA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Iſtijus peeluḑſe\npreeſch ta KUNGA/ un fazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak KUNGS Zebnot tu\nIſraēta Deews! kas tu pahr\nteem Kerubim fehdi/ tu vats\nweens eſſi tas Deews wiſtu\nSeimnes Walsību/ tu eſſi to\nDebvesi un to Seimni darrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Aegrees ak KUNGS!\ntawn Auſi/ un klaſti/ atdarr\nak KUNGS! tawas Azzis/ un\nraugi/ un klaufi wiſtus Wahrdus\nSaneriba/ ko wiſch irr fuhtijs\nto dſhwu Deewu apinehdiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Teescham KUNGS/ tee\nKehnini no Affrijas irr wiſfas\nSeimnes Mallas ar wiſkahin\nwinnu Walsīm pobſtifschi/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un irr winno Deewus\nUgguni mettuſchi/ jo tee ne btja\nDeewi / bet Zilweko Rohkas\nDarbs/ Kohks un Aktwins/ ta-\npehz irr tee tohs famattaifschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad ak KUNGS\nmuhfu Deews! iṣglahb mahs\nno winna Rohkas/ tad fajuttibe\nwiſtas Walsības wirs Sem-\nmes/ tewi ween eſſani to KUN-\nGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhtijs Eſaijuſ A-\nmeza Dehts us Iſtiju/ un likt\nfazzibt: Ta fakta tas KUNGS\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schis irr tas Wahrdā/\nko tas KUNGS prett winau\nirr runnajs: Ta Zumprawa Zi-\nanas Meita nizzina tewi/ wiṣ-\nka apniehd tewiṣ/ ta Jerusale-\nmes Meita kratta to Galwu tew\npakkat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ko eſſi tu apfinehjis un\nfaimojis? un prett ko eſſi tu to\nBalji pazehlis? un tawas Azzis\naugsti uszehlis prett to Swehtu\neekſch Iſraēta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zaur taiweem Kalpeem ef-\nfi tu to Kungu aptnehdījs un\nfazzījs : Zaur manno Ratto\nPulku eſmu es uskahpte us to\nKalnu Augſtumeem/ us Libba-\nnus Sahnecm / un iszirtifchu\nwiṣna augsts Zeedra-Kohkus /\nun wiṣna islaſitas Preedes/ an\nnahſchu lihos patt winna Wirš-\nGallam/ winna Karmeta Me-\nscha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es eſmu razzis un Uh-\ndeni dſehris/ un ar fawahm Beh-\ndahui wiſfas Uppes to apsehsto\nWeetu isschahwejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj tu ne eſſi dsirdejs/\nka es jaw fenn to papreeksch eſ-\nmu darrijs? jo wezzos Laikos et-\nmu es to apachincees/ nu eſmu\neſ to lizzis nahkt / ka tew bij\nbuht/ kam bij stiprus Pilſfahtus\nispobſtiht / un par pohſahm\nAktimu-Kohpahm darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz bija winnu Ee-\nH\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
